<item>
            <title>[HIVE-16388] LLAP: Log rotation for daemon, history and gc files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-16388</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;GC logs need to be rotated by date.&lt;br/&gt;
LLAP daemon history logs as well&lt;br/&gt;
Ideally, the daemon.out file needs the same&lt;br/&gt;
Need to be able to download relevant logfiles for a time window.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
