                            <comment id="15960328" author="sseth" created="Fri, 7 Apr 2017 06:04:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is it possible to use a custom log level instead of WARN for the daemon startup message? WARN can be confused for an error. (Nice to have more than anything else).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
